data.meta_description:
63 likes, 0 comments - dr.kavithagautham on July 15, 2023: "Delay in pregnancy can be a challenging and frustrating experience for individuals or couples who are trying to conceive. There are various factors that can contribute to delays in achieving pregnancy, and it is important to understand these reasons to seek appropriate medical advice and support. 40% cases are due to issues in women, 40% cases might be caused by issues in men and the remaining 20% might be due to sexual health issues between the couple. 
In this #doctalks , we will explore some common reasons in women that may cause delayed pregnancy.
